import React from 'react'
import {AppBar, Box, Tab, Tabs, Toolbar, Typography} from "@mui/material"

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <AppBar position='sticky'>
      <Toolbar>
        <Typography variant='h4'>
          Podcasts
        </Typography>
        <Box>
          <Tabs value>
            <Tab label="1"/>
            <Tab label="2"/>
            <Tab label="3"/>
          </Tabs>
        </Box>
      </Toolbar>
    </AppBar>
  )
}

export default Header
